---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Kingsfoil Health"
  description="How Kingsfoil Health collects, uses, and protects your personal information."
  canonicalPath="/privacy"
>

<!-- PAGE HERO -->
<section class="page-hero" aria-label="Page introduction">
  <div class="eyebrow">Privacy Policy</div>
  <h1>Your privacy <em>matters</em></h1>
  <p class="page-hero-sub">How we collect, use, and protect your personal information.</p>
</section>

<!-- PROSE CONTENT -->
<section class="section prose-section" aria-label="Privacy policy content">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="prose">
      <p class="last-updated">Last updated: March 25, 2026</p>

      <p>Resilience Stack, LLC, doing business as Kingsfoil Health ("we," "us," or "our"), operates the website kingsfoilhealth.com. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website or engage with our services.</p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <h3>Information you provide</h3>
      <p>When you fill out a contact form, download a resource, or subscribe to our newsletter, we may collect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Name (first and last)</li>
        <li>Work email address</li>
        <li>Company name</li>
        <li>Job title or role</li>
        <li>Company size</li>
        <li>Any additional information you choose to include in a message</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Information collected automatically</h3>
      <p>When you visit our website, we may automatically collect certain information, including:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>IP address</li>
        <li>Browser type and version</li>
        <li>Operating system</li>
        <li>Pages visited and time spent on each page</li>
        <li>Referring website or source</li>
        <li>Device type</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Respond to your inquiries and provide requested information</li>
        <li>Send you resources you've requested (reports, guides, tools)</li>
        <li>Deliver newsletter content you've subscribed to</li>
        <li>Improve our website and services</li>
        <li>Understand how visitors use our website</li>
        <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do not sell your personal information. We do not use your information for purposes unrelated to the services described on this website.</p>

      <h2>Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
      <p>Our website may use cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance your browsing experience and collect analytics data. These may include:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Essential cookies</strong> — Required for basic site functionality</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics cookies</strong> — Help us understand how visitors interact with our website (e.g., Google Analytics)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>You can control cookies through your browser settings. Disabling cookies may affect some website functionality.</p>

      <h2>Third Parties</h2>
      <p>We may share your information with trusted third-party service providers who assist us in operating our website and conducting our business, including:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Form processing</strong> — To receive and manage contact form submissions</li>
        <li><strong>Email delivery</strong> — To send newsletters and requested resources</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics</strong> — To understand website usage patterns</li>
      </ul>
      <p>These service providers are obligated to keep your information confidential and use it only for the purposes for which we disclose it to them.</p>

      <h2>Data Security</h2>
      <p>We implement reasonable administrative, technical, and physical security measures to protect your personal information. However, no method of transmission over the Internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access the personal information we hold about you</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your personal information</li>
        <li>Opt out of marketing communications at any time</li>
        <li>Object to the processing of your personal information</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To exercise any of these rights, please contact us using the information below.</p>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us:</p>
      <p><strong>Resilience Stack, LLC (dba Kingsfoil Health)</strong><br>
      Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@kingsfoilhealth.com">privacy@kingsfoilhealth.com</a></p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When we do, we will revise the "Last updated" date at the top of this page. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically to stay informed about how we are protecting your information.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
/* PAGE HERO */
.page-hero{padding:72px var(--section-pad-x) 64px;text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.page-hero::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 60% at 30% 80%, rgba(252,244,215,0.35) 0%, transparent 50%),radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 50% at 70% 70%, rgba(212,238,234,0.2) 0%, transparent 50%);pointer-events:none}
.page-hero .eyebrow{color:var(--elm-600);position:relative;z-index:1}
.page-hero h1{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,60px);font-weight:700;line-height:1.08;letter-spacing:-0.03em;max-width:720px;margin:0 auto 20px;position:relative;z-index:1}
.page-hero h1 em{font-style:italic;background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--elm-600), var(--elm-500));-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text}
.page-hero-sub{font-size:clamp(16px,1.6vw,19px);line-height:1.65;color:var(--nero-500);max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;position:relative;z-index:1}

/* PROSE */
.prose-section{background:var(--warm-linen)}
.prose{max-width:720px;margin:0 auto}
.prose .last-updated{font-size:14px;color:var(--nero-400);margin-bottom:40px;padding-bottom:24px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--nero-200)}
.prose h2{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:clamp(22px,2.5vw,28px);font-weight:700;line-height:1.2;margin:48px 0 16px}
.prose h3{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:18px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.3;margin:32px 0 12px}
.prose p{font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;color:var(--nero-600);margin-bottom:16px}
.prose ul{margin:0 0 20px 24px;padding:0}
.prose li{font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;color:var(--nero-600);margin-bottom:8px}
.prose li strong{color:var(--nero-800)}
.prose a{color:var(--elm-600);text-decoration:underline;transition:color var(--t-fast)}
.prose a:hover{color:var(--elm-700)}

/* FOOTER */
.footer{background:var(--nero-900);color:var(--nero-400);border-top:1px solid var(--nero-800);padding:64px var(--section-pad-x) 32px;font-size:14px}
.footer-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:48px;max-width:var(--inner-max);margin:0 auto}
.footer-brand{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:var(--elm-400);margin-bottom:12px}
.footer-tagline{font-style:italic;color:var(--nero-500);margin-bottom:12px;font-size:14px}
.footer p{line-height:1.6;max-width:280px}
.footer-col h4{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--nero-500);margin-bottom:16px}
.footer-col a{display:block;color:var(--nero-400);text-decoration:none;margin-bottom:10px;transition:color var(--t-fast)}.footer-col a:hover{color:var(--elm-400)}
.footer-bottom{max-width:var(--inner-max);margin:48px auto 0;padding-top:24px;border-top:1px solid var(--nero-800);font-size:12px;color:var(--nero-600);display:flex;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.footer-bottom a{color:var(--nero-500);text-decoration:none;transition:color var(--t-fast)}.footer-bottom a:hover{color:var(--elm-400)}

@media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){*,*::before,*::after{animation-duration:0.01ms!important;animation-iteration-count:1!important;transition-duration:0.01ms!important}html{scroll-behavior:auto}}
@media(max-width:768px){
  :root{--section-pad-y:80px;--section-pad-x:24px}
  .nav{padding:0 24px;height:64px}.nav-links{display:none}.nav-cta:not(.nav-overlay .nav-cta){display:none}.nav-toggle{display:block}
  .page-hero{padding:48px 24px 56px}
  .footer-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:32px}
}
@media(max-width:420px){:root{--section-pad-x:16px;--section-pad-y:64px}.page-hero{padding:40px 16px 48px}.footer-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
</style>
